					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I was dreading the revelation that this was one of those &quot;by reading this SCP you BECOME anomalous&quot; skips, where the anomaly itself is designed around the format screw. I was delighted to instead find out that I wasn't the SCP but the document itself was designed to trap somebody else. This is what format screws should be!</p> 
				 	]]>
