				<title>Re: Nice SCP.</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5393002/scp-3393#post-3731686</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 08 Mar 2018 05:04:30 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>sirpudding</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>348648</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>You may want to read it again. The effect is that the details of the SCP are impossible to <em>remember</em>. So it's clear from context that &quot;mnestic&quot; is meant. If you want to counteract an effect that causes <em>forgetfulness</em>, you should take a drug that helps you to <em>remember</em>, not one that makes you <em>forget</em>.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
